<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Longform Factory <%= versionLabel %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/app.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="dashboard-shell">
      <aside class="dashboard-sidebar home-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-brand home-brand">
          <div class="brand-mark">LF</div>
          <div>
            <p class="brand-title">Longform</p>
            <p class="brand-sub">자동 공장 <%= versionLabel %></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="sidebar-menu home-nav">
          <% homeNav.forEach((item) => { %>
            <a class="menu-item home-nav-item <%= item.active ? 'active' : '' %>" href="<%= item.href %>">
              <span class="menu-dot"></span>
              <div>
                <strong><%= item.label %></strong>
                <span class="home-nav-caption"><%= item.shortLabel %></span>
              </div>
            </a>
          <% }) %>
        </nav>

        <section class="sidebar-note">
          <p class="eyebrow">기본 흐름</p>
          <ul class="sidebar-list workflow-list">
            <li>1. 주제 설정</li>
            <li>2. 소재 발굴</li>
            <li>3. 대본 작성</li>
            <li>4. 장면 편집</li>
            <li>5. 렌더 결과</li>
            <li>6. 업로드 연동</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>

      <main class="dashboard-main">
        <% if (activeHomeSection === 'dashboard') { %>
          <section class="hero-board home-hero">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Dashboard</p>
              <h1>롱폼 자동 공장 운영 화면</h1>
              <p class="sub">주제 발굴부터 대본, 장면, 렌더, 업로드까지 한 화면 흐름으로 관리합니다.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-stats hero-stats-wide">
              <article class="stat-card accent">
                <span class="stat-label">버전</span>
                <strong><%= versionLabel %></strong>
              </article>
              <article class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-label">채널 수</span>
                <strong><%= channels.length %></strong>
              </article>
              <article class="stat-card">
                <span class="stat-label">프로젝트 수</span>
                <strong><%= projects.length %></strong>
              </article>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dashboard-grid home-grid">
            <section class="dashboard-column main-column">
              <article class="dashboard-card spotlight-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Quick Start</p>
                    <h2>바로 시작</h2>
                  </div>
                  <a class="result-link" href="/workspace/create">새 프로젝트 열기</a>
                </div>
                <div class="spotlight-grid">
                  <div class="soft-panel">
                    <h3>주제부터 대본까지 자동</h3>
                    <p>프로젝트를 만든 뒤 자동 버튼 한 번으로 소재 수집과 대본 초안을 만듭니다.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="soft-panel">
                    <h3>수동 보정 가능</h3>
                    <p>각 단계 화면에서 주제, 리서치, 대본, 장면을 직접 수정할 수 있습니다.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>

              <article class="dashboard-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Recent</p>
                    <h2>최근 프로젝트</h2>
                  </div>
                  <a class="result-link" href="/workspace/projects">전체 보기</a>
                </div>

                <div class="project-board">
                  <% if (!projects.length) { %>
                    <div class="empty-board">
                      <strong>아직 프로젝트가 없습니다.</strong>
                      <p>새 프로젝트 화면에서 첫 워크플로우를 생성하면 여기 표시됩니다.</p>
                    </div>
                  <% } %>

                  <% projects.slice(0, 4).forEach((project) => { %>
                    <a class="project-tile" href="/projects/<%= project.id %>/topic">
                      <div>
                        <strong><%= project.topic %></strong>
                        <p><%= project.language %> · <%= project.tone %> · <%= project.format %></p>
                      </div>
                      <span class="badge <%= project.status %>"><%= project.status %></span>
                    </a>
                  <% }) %>
                </div>
              </article>
            </section>

            <aside class="dashboard-column side-column">
              <article class="dashboard-card compact-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Flow</p>
                    <h2>작업 단계</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-card">
                  <div class="timeline-item done">
                    <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>주제 설정</strong>
                      <p>언어, 톤, 비율, 채널과 예약값을 먼저 고정합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-item">
                    <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>리서치와 대본</strong>
                      <p>자동 수집과 자동 대본 생성 후 바로 수동 보정합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="timeline-item">
                    <span class="timeline-dot"></span>
                    <div>
                      <strong>장면과 렌더</strong>
                      <p>장면 단위 재생성과 최종 렌더 결과를 같은 흐름에서 확인합니다.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </aside>
          </section>
        <% } %>

        <% if (activeHomeSection === 'create') { %>
          <section class="hero-board home-hero">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Create</p>
              <h1>새 프로젝트 만들기</h1>
              <p class="sub">주제와 기본 설정을 먼저 만들고, 이후 프로젝트 상세 화면에서 단계별로 작업합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dashboard-grid home-grid single-main-grid">
            <section class="dashboard-column main-column">
              <article class="dashboard-card form-page-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">New Workflow</p>
                    <h2>프로젝트 생성</h2>
                  </div>
                  <span class="pill">Auto + Manual</span>
                </div>

                <form class="form-grid dashboard-form" action="/projects" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                  <label>주제
                    <input type="text" name="topic" placeholder="예: 수면의 질을 높이는 습관" required />
                  </label>

                  <label>언어
                    <select name="language">
                      <option value="ko">한국어</option>
                      <option value="en">영어</option>
                      <option value="ja">일본어</option>
                    </select>
                  </label>

                  <label>톤
                    <input type="text" name="tone" value="정보형" />
                  </label>

                  <label>화면 비율
                    <select name="format">
                      <option value="portrait">세로형 9:16</option>
                      <option value="landscape">가로형 16:9</option>
                    </select>
                  </label>

                  <label>채널
                    <select name="channelId">
                      <option value="">선택 안 함</option>
                      <% channels.forEach((channel) => { %>
                        <option value="<%= channel.id %>"><%= channel.name %></option>
                      <% }) %>
                    </select>
                  </label>

                  <label>예약 시작
                    <input type="datetime-local" name="scheduledAt" />
                  </label>

                  <label class="wide">추가 지시
                    <input type="text" name="customPrompt" placeholder="예: 차분하고 신뢰감 있게" />
                  </label>

                  <label>스타일 레퍼런스
                    <input type="file" name="styleReference" accept="image/*" />
                  </label>

                  <label>BGM 파일
                    <input type="file" name="bgmFile" accept="audio/*" />
                  </label>

                  <label class="wide">워터마크
                    <input type="file" name="watermarkFile" accept="image/*" />
                  </label>

                  <div class="wide form-actions">
                    <button type="submit">프로젝트 시작</button>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </article>
            </section>
          </section>
        <% } %>

        <% if (activeHomeSection === 'channels') { %>
          <section class="hero-board home-hero">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Channels</p>
              <h1>업로드 채널 관리</h1>
              <p class="sub">유튜브 업로드용 웹훅 채널을 등록하고 현재 연결 상태를 관리합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dashboard-grid home-grid">
            <section class="dashboard-column main-column">
              <article class="dashboard-card form-page-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Add Channel</p>
                    <h2>채널 등록</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <form class="form-grid single-form" action="/channels" method="post">
                  <label>채널 이름
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="메인 유튜브 채널" />
                  </label>

                  <label>플랫폼
                    <input type="text" name="platform" value="youtube" />
                  </label>

                  <label>업로드 웹훅 URL
                    <input type="text" name="uploadWebhookUrl" placeholder="n8n webhook URL" />
                  </label>

                  <div class="form-actions">
                    <button type="submit">채널 저장</button>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </article>
            </section>

            <aside class="dashboard-column side-column">
              <article class="dashboard-card compact-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">Saved Channels</p>
                    <h2>등록 채널</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="project-board">
                  <% if (!channels.length) { %>
                    <div class="empty-board">
                      <strong>등록된 채널이 없습니다.</strong>
                      <p>먼저 웹훅 채널을 추가한 뒤 프로젝트에 연결하십시오.</p>
                    </div>
                  <% } %>

                  <% channels.forEach((channel) => { %>
                    <div class="project-tile static-tile">
                      <div>
                        <strong><%= channel.name %></strong>
                        <p><%= channel.platform %></p>
                      </div>
                      <span class="badge"><%= channel.upload_webhook_url ? 'webhook' : 'local' %></span>
                    </div>
                  <% }) %>
                </div>
              </article>
            </aside>
          </section>
        <% } %>

        <% if (activeHomeSection === 'projects') { %>
          <section class="hero-board home-hero">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>
              <h1>프로젝트 목록</h1>
              <p class="sub">생성한 프로젝트를 다시 열어서 단계별 편집 화면으로 이동합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="dashboard-grid home-grid single-main-grid">
            <section class="dashboard-column main-column">
              <article class="dashboard-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div>
                    <p class="eyebrow">All Projects</p>
                    <h2>전체 프로젝트</h2>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="project-board">
                  <% if (!projects.length) { %>
                    <div class="empty-board">
                      <strong>아직 프로젝트가 없습니다.</strong>
                      <p>새 프로젝트 화면에서 첫 워크플로우를 생성하십시오.</p>
                    </div>
                  <% } %>

                  <% projects.forEach((project) => { %>
                    <a class="project-tile project-tile-large" href="/projects/<%= project.id %>/topic">
                      <div>
                        <strong><%= project.topic %></strong>
                        <p><%= project.language %> · <%= project.tone %> · <%= project.format %></p>
                      </div>
                      <span class="badge <%= project.status %>"><%= project.status %></span>
                    </a>
                  <% }) %>
                </div>
              </article>
            </section>
          </section>
        <% } %>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
